race.description: Hydraulink Parkes & Forbes / Kennards Hire Handicap
race.comment: CHARLIE MAGIC (4) left himself with far too much to do fresh but was better last time when much more prominent. Nearing peak now and is drawn to advantage. Should be poised to strike when they quicken. HOUDINI SPIRIT (9) gave a sight here last time, leading until late before finishing fifth and beaten a tick under 2L. Fitter and is drawn perfectly. Will take plenty of reeling in if left alone in front. AEROBATIC WARRIOR (11) made the perfect return at Queanbeyan when scoring by a neck over the 900m. Tougher this time is a likely improver worth including. CUMBOOGLE (1) strips fitter and will appreciate the drop in grade. Don't underestimate.
